    "text": "<@U089PPWPXT9> I didn’t know about Pipeworld nor Figma widgets. Thanks for pointing me at them! :pray:\n\nLike <@UBKNXPBAB> says, Figma’s widgets seem to be black boxes, whereas the objects in Scrappy are more like building blocks — closer to Alan Kay’s original meaning of “object” in object-oriented programming (Smalltalk, Squeak).",
