                "type": "user",
                "user_id": "UBKNXPBAB"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " says, Figma’s widgets seem to be black boxes, whereas the objects in Scrappy are more like building blocks — closer to Alan Kay’s original meaning of “object” in object-oriented programming (Smalltalk, Squeak)."
              }
